NFL SIMULATOR — ROADMAP
Last Updated: June 18, 2026
Repository: https://github.com/blakewhitney3163/NFLSimulator
================================================================================

TIER 1 — Makes the sim feel alive (highest impact)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Game Simulation Improvements — more realistic box score detail, scoring
  distribution, and play-by-play narrative hooks in the sim engine.

Milestone Notifications — pop-ups when a player hits 10,000 career yards,
  breaks a franchise record, or posts a historic single-season stat line.
  Ties directly into the news feed.

TIER 2 — Adds strategic depth
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Contract Negotiation Depth — multi-year offer counters, holdout mechanic,
  dead cap penalties on early releases. Contracts feel too simple today.

Coaching Staff System — OC/DC coordinators with ratings that affect team
  performance. Hiring and firing adds another management layer.

Draft Combine / Deeper Scouting — measurables (40 time, bench press) that
  hint at potential. Ties into the existing 25-scout scouting system.

Practice Squad Development — PS players develop week to week and become
  genuine roster contributors rather than static depth fillers.

Schemes — offensive and defensive scheme selection that shapes team identity
  and influences sim output (run-heavy, pass-heavy, zone vs man, etc.).

TIER 3 — Polish & replayability
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Player Editor — manually edit player ratings, position, age, dev trait.

Team Editor — edit team name, city, colors, conference/division.

Playoff UI Update — bracket-style visual for the playoff tree with game
  scores, seeds, and champion display.

Multiple Save Files — essential for a long franchise game.

Historical Mode — load real NFL rosters from a specific year and simulate
  forward from that point.

League Customization — expansion teams, relocation, custom team names.
